column11: HIGH;  31 FEET 4 INCHES AT DEPTH OF SURVEY.

column2: Anchor depth 31'.  Sept 12th + 19th-cloudy + windy all week-no readings.
Lake depth 33'.  Lousy weather past 10 days.  Usually try to sample each Tuesday.
Ice off May 24th-+ weather conditions for monitoring were very "iffy". high winds- etc. rain.
Weather cloudy and rainy but today was warm and sunny.
Took reading after a rain and thunderstorm the evening before. a bit riled up.
Weather bad the past 2 weeks- either too windy or rainy.
Weather bad-cloudy + windy + rain the past 2 weeks.
Too early to swim.  Ice out April 21.  Weather has been windy and rainy- unsuitable for monitoring.  Hope to be able to monitor every week.
Weather bad all of May.  High winds- rainy and cloudy.
Finally got a clear day without too much wind.  Water is gradually clearing up.
Finally getting nice weather to pursue our project.
Weather has been windy or cloudy.
Weather has been windy and cloudy.
Weather finally cleared up after 2 weeks of clouds- wind and rain.
Weather finally cleared enough and no wind.  A very nice day!
Finally got a clear day without too much wind.
Lake slightly cloudy due to needles and leaves falling.  Weather is 76 degrees.
Nice clear and calm day.  Ideal for monitoring.
Partly sunny- slight breeze- nice day.  Saw one loon and some ducks.
Overcast- breezy- water looks murky green.
Partly cloudy - lake calm - murky green.
Blue skys and breezy. Very hot and humid with lots of flys. No activity on lake.
Most sunny. Warm but not so humid. Swimmers on lake.
Mostly sunny with slight breeze. Warm and humid with
Sunny day with blue skys. Beautiful weather. Slight
Water very calm like glass. Blue skys and no clouds.
Slight breeze. Blue skys. No actiivity on lake.
Sunny day-some fisherman on the lake and loons
Mostly sunny- slight beeze. No activity on lake.
sunny and warm. Some swimmers on lake.
Slight breeze but sunny. Loons on lake.
Mostly cloudy with slight breeze. Lake quiet not much
Mostly sunny and calm. Beautiful day with temperatures
Calm. Starting to see some change in tree color. lake
mostly sunny with a slight breeze- lake quiet
mostly cloudy and no breeze. Loons on lake. Lots of pollen in water.
Calm with no breeze. Very warm and humid. Boaters on lake.
Partly cloudy with slight breeze. Swimmers on lake.
Beautiful Day. Blue sky and no wind. Swimmers on lake.
Blue sky. Feels like fall with Temperatures in the low 60's. No activity on lake.
Cooler with slight breeze. No activity on the lake.
Warm day. Very nice out. Lake Calm.
Blue skies and calm. Eagle sitting in pine. Beautiful fall colors.
Blue skies and temperature in 80s. Two loons and swimmers on lake.
Beautiful day - sunny.  Swimmers on lake.
Mostly sunny- lake very quiet.  Lake level very low.
Leaves starting to change color.  Lake quiet.  Lake level very low.
blue skies and warm temps- few boats on lake
mostly sunny- nice day- loons on lake
mostly sunny- with a slight breeze. lake quiet
hot and humid- blue skies and breezy
clear skies and temp in high 70's- swimmers on lake
Beautiful day- starting to feel like fall
Calm day. Mostly sunny. Saw loon. Water unseasonably warm. Lots of pollen.
Slight breeze. Blue skies. 80 degrees. Water low. Swimmer and boaters.
Sunny. No rain. Temperature in the mid 70's.
Sunny. Lake getting really low. Dock mostly out of the water.
water level up from last fall. Sunny.
Calm and sunny. Pollen on lake.
Sunny with temperatures in the low 70's. Quiet on lake.
Sunny and breezy. Pontoon boat on lake.
Sunny. Slight wind from SW. Temperature in the 80's. Lake is low.
Blue skys.  Almost cloudless.  Warm in the 60's.
Hot and humid.  Upper 80's. Still with no breeze.  Lots of algae.  Loon on lake.
Warm and mostly sunny.  Breezy with lots of pollen in water.
Breezy and partly sunny.  Low to mid 70's.  Lake is quiet.
Water level very low.  Partly sunny.  Swimmers adn boat on teh lake.
Cool.  Mid 60's.  Sunny with blue skys and no clouds.  No activity on lake.
Overcast and cool.  Lake level very low.  Starting to feel like fall.

Blue skies with few clouds. Lake level is extremely low. The weather is beautiful in the mid 60's but feel like 70's with the sun. Blue skies with few clouds. Water level is extremely low. Beautiful day in the mid 60's but feels like 70's in the sun.
Overcast; water level up from last Fall; slight breeze.
sunny with light wind and low 70's air temp; 8 loons on the lake; no recreational activity on the lake
partly cloudy; no wind; no recreational activity; calm water
filtered sunlight- north wind at 5-10 mph- slight wave- significant Southern Naiad growth
partly sunny- west wind at 15 mph- slight wave at  less than 1 foot- significant growth of Southern Naiad at many locations around the lake
clear sky- slight wave- 10 mph wind from west- no visible Southern Naiad growth- sunny
partly cloudy sky- low 40's air temp- calm wind- calm water- no visible weed growth
clear sunny sky- clear water- 60's air temp- calm wind- calm water surface- no visible weed growth
partly cloudy- 70's air temp- calm wind- calm water- no visible weed growth
sunny day- 60's air temp- calm water- slight green color in water- no visible Southern Naiad growth- used Phelps meter
sunny- very slight wave- light west wind- exactly 2 weeks after ice out- very brown water color apparently from tannic acid- surface colored by pollen and maple flowers
light breeze- partly cloudy- 75 degrees air temp- slight wave- clear but brown water
light breeze- clear sky- 72 degree air temp. slight wave- clear but brown water
light breeze- overcast sky- slight wave
partly cloudy- calm water- no wind- exactly one week after ice out
partly cloudy- calm water- no wind- exactly one week after ice out- slight ripple
cloudy- slight wave action- SE wind at about 10 mph- rain earlier- break in rain during testing
sunny to partly cloudy- moderate wind and chop- NW wind
clear and sunny- calm winds and waves- significant rain the night before testing- mid 70's air temp
65 degree air temp. moderate wind- partly sunny- slight chop on water
sunny- moderate wind- slight chop- cloudless sky- 70 degree air temp
thunderstorm overnight- cloudy- 70 air temp. calm water-
